{
  "texts": [
    "Fine-Tuning on a Regression Task.",
    "Given that we want to predict the averaged user-standardized rating (stars) of a recipe, we formulate the prediction stage as a regression task: for any given recipe denoted as x, the predictive model should output a real-valued star rating symbolized as S(x).",
    "Thus, we fine-tune RELEXset-MLM to predict the number of stars of recipes in RELEXset.",
    "We will refer to the obtained model as RELEXset-Predictor 4.",
    "The model has six transformer layers, each with a hidden size of 768, and employs 12 attention heads."
  ]
}